<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Your OpenRoaming Profile has Expired</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
</head>
<body class="bg-[#080D4A] font-sans text-gray-800">
<div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <div class="max-w-md mx-auto bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg overflow-hidden">
        <div class="bg-[#e53935] text-white text-center p-6">
            <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold">Your OpenRoaming Profile has Expired</h1>
        </div>

        <div class="p-6">
            <p class="text-lg mb-4">
                Your OpenRoaming profile has expired.
            </p>
            <p class="text-lg mb-4">
                To get a new profile, please follow these simple steps:
            </p>
            <ol class="mt-4 text-lg list-decimal list-inside space-y-3">
                <li>
                    Click <a class="font-bold text-[#7BBA29] underline"
                             href="{{ absolute_url(path('app_landing')) }}">here</a> to access the OpenRoaming portal.
                </li>
                <li>Log in with your credentials.</li>
                <li>Inside the portal, download a new profile.</li>
            </ol>
            <p class="mt-6 text-lg">
                Thank you,<br>
                <strong>{{ supportTeam }}</strong> Team
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-gray-100 text-center p-6">
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">
                If you have any questions, feel free to contact our support team at
                <a href="mailto:{{ contactEmail }}" class="text-[#0045ad] underline">{{ contactEmail }}</a>.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
